On the other hand, with the assistance of the most recent computer tools, it would be a question of minutes.
This is why almost 100% of experts use this type of systems.
Providers of services and solutions for assessment and maintenance are dedicated to the collection of information provided by manufacturers to then process and offer to their customers in the form of a useful tool.
In Spain, Audatex of the North American group Solera is the leading company; 80% of the estimates are made with its products.
Other companies competing in the field of evaluation tools and the development of information on the sector are GtMotive and Eurotax.
Working with the data provided by manufacturers is far from simple.
According to Eduardo Velázquez, Managing Director of Audatex, the company in Spain with 63 manufacturers and importers, and each of them provides them with information in a different format.
Furthermore, the amount of data to be processed is constantly increasing, so in the past five years more versions, variants and motors have been launched than in the past fifteen years.
When a new car comes out of the market, these companies get to work.
This is a very hard work because each of the thousand parts of the vehicle must be cataloged and enrolled in price.
Furthermore, a “intelligent” graphic image of each model can be established, on which you can click on the different parts of a tourist car.
If this is a massively sold model, work can be ready in a week if the process is moving very quickly.
