Four-step garage quote
With the Auda-Taller tool, the Audatex company ensures that the user gets a quote in only four steps: identifying the vehicle, searching for the spare part, creating a quote and generating it.
Ease of use is an essential part of these systems, especially to convince the older professionals who, in a larger amount, are reactive to the use of new management techniques.
The database includes 1,034 vehicles, including 666 tourism, 109 all-terrains, 137 motorcycles, 78 vans and 44 trucks.
